{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.1","label":"","reference":"Job 8:1","prev_osis_id":"Job.007.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Discours de Bildad \u00e0 Job<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-7: cf. (Job 34:10-19; 22:21-30. Ps 92:13, etc.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.8.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Bildad de Schuach prit la parole et dit:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.2","name":"Job 8:2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.7.21","name":"Job 7:21","id":"fra-LSG:Job.7.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.2","label":"","reference":"Job 8:2","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Jusqu\u2019\u00e0 quand veux-tu discourir de la sorte,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et les paroles de ta bouche seront-elles un vent imp\u00e9tueux?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.3","name":"Job 8:3","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.1","name":"Job 8:1","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.3","label":"","reference":"Job 8:3","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>\n    Dieu renverserait-il le droit?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Le Tout-Puissant renverserait-il la justice?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.4","name":"Job 8:4","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.2","name":"Job 8:2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.4","label":"","reference":"Job 8:4","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Si tes fils ont p\u00e9ch\u00e9 contre lui,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il les a livr\u00e9s \u00e0 leur p\u00e9ch\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.5","name":"Job 8:5","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.3","name":"Job 8:3","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.5","label":"","reference":"Job 8:5","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>\n    Mais toi, si tu as recours \u00e0 Dieu,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Si tu implores le Tout-Puissant;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.6","name":"Job 8:6","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.4","name":"Job 8:4","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.6","label":"","reference":"Job 8:6","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Si tu es juste et droit,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Certainement alors il veillera sur toi,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et rendra le bonheur \u00e0 ton innocente demeure;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.7","name":"Job 8:7","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.5","name":"Job 8:5","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.7","label":"","reference":"Job 8:7","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Ton ancienne prosp\u00e9rit\u00e9 semblera peu de chose,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Celle qui t\u2019est r\u00e9serv\u00e9e sera bien plus grande.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.8","name":"Job 8:8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.6","name":"Job 8:6","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.8","label":"","reference":"Job 8:8","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.009,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 8-22: cf. Job 20:4-9. Ps 37:16, etc.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>\n    Interroge ceux des g\u00e9n\u00e9rations pass\u00e9es,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Sois attentif \u00e0 l\u2019exp\u00e9rience de leurs p\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.9","name":"Job 8:9","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.7","name":"Job 8:7","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.9","label":"","reference":"Job 8:9","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>\n    Car nous sommes d\u2019hier, et nous ne savons rien,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Nos jours sur la terre ne sont qu\u2019une ombre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.10","name":"Job 8:10","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.8","name":"Job 8:8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.10","label":"","reference":"Job 8:10","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Ils t\u2019instruiront, ils te parleront,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils tireront de leur c\u0153ur ces sentences:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.11","name":"Job 8:11","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.9","name":"Job 8:9","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.11","label":"","reference":"Job 8:11","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Le jonc cro\u00eet-il sans marais?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Le roseau cro\u00eet-il sans humidit\u00e9?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.12","name":"Job 8:12","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.10","name":"Job 8:10","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.12","label":"","reference":"Job 8:12","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>\n    Encore vert et sans qu\u2019on le coupe,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il s\u00e8che plus vite que toutes les herbes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.13","name":"Job 8:13","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.11","name":"Job 8:11","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.13","label":"","reference":"Job 8:13","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Ainsi arrive-t-il \u00e0 tous ceux qui oublient Dieu,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Et l\u2019esp\u00e9rance de l\u2019impie p\u00e9rira.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.14","name":"Job 8:14","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.12","name":"Job 8:12","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.14","label":"","reference":"Job 8:14","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Son assurance est bris\u00e9e,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Son soutien est une toile d\u2019araign\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.15","name":"Job 8:15","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.13","name":"Job 8:13","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.15","label":"","reference":"Job 8:15","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Il s\u2019appuie sur sa maison, et elle n\u2019est pas ferme;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il s\u2019y cramponne, et elle ne r\u00e9siste pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.16","name":"Job 8:16","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.14","name":"Job 8:14","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.16","label":"","reference":"Job 8:16","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Dans toute sa vigueur, en plein soleil,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il \u00e9tend ses rameaux sur son jardin,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.17","name":"Job 8:17","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.15","name":"Job 8:15","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.17","label":"","reference":"Job 8:17","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Il entrelace ses racines parmi les pierres,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il p\u00e9n\u00e8tre jusque dans les murailles;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.18","name":"Job 8:18","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.16","name":"Job 8:16","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.18","label":"","reference":"Job 8:18","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>L\u2019arrache-t-on du lieu qu\u2019il occupe,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ce lieu le renie: Je ne t\u2019ai point connu!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.19","name":"Job 8:19","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.17","name":"Job 8:17","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.19","label":"","reference":"Job 8:19","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Telles sont les d\u00e9lices que ses voies lui procurent.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Puis sur le m\u00eame sol d\u2019autres s\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8vent apr\u00e8s lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.20","name":"Job 8:20","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.18","name":"Job 8:18","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.20","label":"","reference":"Job 8:20","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Non, Dieu ne rejette point l\u2019homme int\u00e8gre,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et il ne prot\u00e8ge point les m\u00e9chants.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.21","name":"Job 8:21","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.19","name":"Job 8:19","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.21","label":"","reference":"Job 8:21","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.008.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Il remplira ta bouche de cris de joie,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et tes l\u00e8vres de chants d\u2019all\u00e9gresse.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.22","name":"Job 8:22","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.20","name":"Job 8:20","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.8.22","label":"","reference":"Job 8:22","prev_osis_id":"Job.008.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.009.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Job.8.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Tes ennemis seront couverts de honte;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">La tente des m\u00e9chants dispara\u00eetra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.8","name":"Job 8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.9.1","name":"Job 9:1","id":"fra-LSG:Job.9.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.8.21","name":"Job 8:21","id":"fra-LSG:Job.8.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+doc